Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic scored nine points in overtime to secure the win
Victor Wembanyama was scoreless and without a rebound in overtime
Michael Porter Jr. added 28 points and 10 rebounds for Denver
Harrison Barnes scored 22 points and Devin Vassell 19 for San Antonio
Post-Match Reflections: Nikola Jokic made sure there were no heroics, scoring nine points in the extra period
Denver's five-man bench accounted for 18 points and 21 rebounds
Miscellaneous Highlights: Zach Collins and Russell Westbrook each received a technical foul in the first quarter after taunting one another, with Westbrook doing so from the bench
